<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title><%= school.name %> 관리자 대시보드 - SchoolHub</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("../partials/admin-header", { school }) %>

  <main class="container">
    <a href="/admin" class="back-link">← 학교 선택으로 돌아가기</a>

    <section class="admin-page-header">
      <div>
        <h1><%= school.name %> 관리자 대시보드</h1>
        <p>
          이 페이지에서는 <strong><%= school.name %></strong>의 게시글, 댓글, 공지사항, 분실물을 관리합니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <% if (school.is_active) { %>
        <span class="notice-school status-approved">활성</span>
      <% } else { %>
        <span class="notice-school status-pending">비활성</span>
      <% } %>
    </section>

    <div class="admin-card-grid">
      <a href="/admin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts/pending" class="admin-card">
        <h2>승인 대기 게시글</h2>
        <p><%= pendingPostsCount %>개</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/admin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/comments/pending" class="admin-card">
        <h2>승인 대기 댓글</h2>
        <p><%= pendingCommentsCount %>개</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/admin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/lost-items/pending" class="admin-card">
        <h2>승인 대기 분실물</h2>
        <p><%= pendingLostItemsCount %>개</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/admin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/reports" class="admin-card">
        <h3>신고 관리</h3>
        <p><%= reportsCount %>개</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/admin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/notices" class="admin-card">
        <h2>공지사항</h2>
        <p><%= noticesCount %>개</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="admin-service-section">
      <div class="admin-service-header">
        <h2>학교 전용 관리 페이지</h2>
        <p>선택한 학교의 데이터만 따로 관리합니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-service-grid">
        <a href="/admin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/board" class="admin-service-card">
          <span>MANAGE</span>
          <h3>게시판 관리</h3>
          <p>
            <%= school.name %>의 게시글과 댓글을 확인하고 관리합니다.
            현재 공개 게시글은 <strong><%= approvedPostsCount %>개</strong>입니다.
          </p>
        </a>

        <a href="/admin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/lost-items" class="admin-service-card">
          <span>MANAGE</span>
          <h3>분실물 관리</h3>
          <p>
            <%= school.name %>의 분실물 등록글을 확인하고 관리합니다.
            전체 분실물은 <strong><%= lostItemsCount %>개</strong>입니다.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include("../partials/admin-footer") %>
</body>
</html>